i was surprised that nimoy played a bad gud. he is best known for playing spock on star trek. if  they are all big names then why does the  movie get bad ratings 



If anyone who is film academicly inclined, it's a horrible movie... plus, it's a specific children's movie, it's not really focused upon the adults of that time, but the kids of the 80's who loved the series. The movie, let alone the Transformers in general is a huge hit to kids. But as a film critic, it's lousy. 
But... who cares about the critics, we love Transformers nonetheless! ;)
